title: Routledge Frequency Dictionary Pack
description:
This is a small portion of the Routledge Frequency Dictionary series. A frequency dictionary lists the most common 5000 words in frequency order and is an invaluable tool for filling gaps in vocabulary.  

These dictionaries are really useful, so I thought it would be good to keep them all in one place.

===================================================================

Book List:

A Frequency Dictionary of Arabic (2011)
A Frequency Dictionary of French (2009)
A Frequency Dictionary of German (2006)
A Frequency Dictionary of Portuguese (2008)
A Frequency Dictionary of Spanish (2006)

Russian Learner's Dictionary: 10000 Words in Frequency Order (1996)

===================================================================
